422
00:52:02,909 --> 00:52:04,369
Jika kau pergi saat aku pergi,...

423
00:52:04,870 --> 00:52:06,788
...mereka akan memburu dan membunuhmu.

424
00:52:06,872 --> 00:52:08,790
Kau paham?

