01:26:27,514 --> 01:26:29,057
Mika!

655
01:26:30,225 --> 01:26:31,768
Tidak!

656
01:26:37,232 --> 01:26:39,234
Banyak anak-anak mengecewakan,...

657
01:26:40,068 --> 01:26:43,196
...tak sepadan dengan usaha
untuk membesarkannya.

658
01:28:00,356 --> 01:28:01,941
Mika.

659
01:28:28,927 --> 01:28:30,845
Astaga, apa yang terjadi?

660
01:28:30,929 --> 01:28:32,639
Dia menyelamatkan nyawaku.

661
01:28:35,600 --> 01:28:36,684
Paramedis!

662
01:28:38,520 --> 01:28:40,104
Paramedis!

