01:28:45,485 --> 01:28:47,612
Dia akan baik-baik saja.

664
01:28:48,738 --> 01:28:50,490
Jantungnya spesial.

665
01:28:52,534 --> 01:28:54,536
Aku butuh paramedis sekarang!

666
01:29:01,751 --> 01:29:04,170
-Apa dia akan selamat?
-Aku tak mengerti.

667
01:29:05,380 --> 01:29:07,674
Dadanya berlubang
sampai ke jantungnya, tapi--

668
01:29:07,757 --> 01:29:10,134
Jantungku di sini.

669
01:30:08,109 --> 01:30:09,569
Ikutlah denganku.

